@zanderso I got more details from the user. He said he was using the app normally and then he blocked the screen. 10 minutes later the unlocked the phone and the app was frozen, unresponsive, he couldn't do anything.

Then he tried several gestures and got to minimize the app. When he came back to the app, the app was flickering.

He's using our release version from the App Store, not TestFlight.
